<% if @enrollment.is_shop? %>
  <div style='width: 400px; margin-left: 50px'>
    <p>
      <%= @person&.first_name %>,<br/><br/>

      This confirms that you're enrolled in the <b><%= @enrollment&.plan&.name %></b> plan offered by your employer.<br/><br/>

      Your monthly premium contribution is <b><%= ActionView::Base.new.number_to_currency @member_group.group_enrollment.employee_cost_total %>.</b> Your employer contributes <b><%= ActionView::Base.new.number_to_currency @member_group.group_enrollment.sponsor_contribution_total %></b> towards your monthly premium.</p><br/><br/>

      Your coverage start date is <b><%= @enrollment.effective_on.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></b>.<br/><br/>

      Thank you for enrolling in coverage through <%= Settings.site.short_name %>.<br/><br/>

      <%= Settings.site.short_name %><<br/>
      <%= Settings.contact_center.short_number %><br/>
      TTY: <%= Settings.contact_center.tty %><br/>
    </p>
  </div>
<% else %>
  <div style='width: 400px; margin-left: 50px'>
    <p>
      <%= @person&.first_name %>,<br>

      This confirms enrollment in <b><%= @enrollment&.plan&.name %></b> through the Individual & Family marketplace.<br>
      <% if @enrollment.applied_aptc_amount.to_f > 0 %>
        Your monthly premium payment is <b><%= ActionView::Base.new.number_to_currency(@plan.total_premium.to_f - @enrollment.applied_aptc_amount.to_f) %></b>.</br>
      <% end %>
      The coverage start date is <b><%= @enrollment.effective_on.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></b>.<br>
      
      You need to make your first monthly premium payment directly to your insurance company to activate your plan. You should receive a bill from your insurance company soon that tells you how to pay and your payment deadline. If you haven’t received a bill in 7-10 days, call your insurance company right away so you don’t miss the deadline and lose your coverage.<br>

      DC Health Link<br>
      (855) 532-5465<br>
      TTY: 711<br>
    </p>
  </div>
<% end %>
